name: Brooke (Club Surrealistica) (2021)
description:
It was raining from the first
And I was dying there of thirst.
So I came in here
And your long-time curse hurts.
But what's worse is this pain in here.
l can't stay in here.
Ain't it clear that l just can't fit.
Yes, I believe that it's time for us to quit.
But when we meet again, introduced as
friends
Please don't let on that you knew me when
I was hungry and it was your world.
- Bob Dylan
